<h1>Edit competition</h1>

<div id="primary">
	<%= render_partial 'forms/competition', @competition %>
</div>

<div id="secondary">
	<h2>Tips</h2>
	<p>Bear in mind that the competition title is used to make
	page addresses. If you change it then the address of all
	the competition's pages will change accordingly.</p>

	<h2>Cancel?</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><%= link_to 'Return to competition', competition_url(:action => 'overview') %></li>
	</ul>
</div>